<html>
  <head>
    <title>Account Activation Request</title>
  </head>
  <body>
      <p>A request to activate your account was received.  If you did not make this request you can ignore this email, no account information has been created or accessed.</p>
      <p>
        <%= link_to 'To activate your account follow this link', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>
      </p>
      <p>If the link above does not work copy and paste the following address into a browser http://$_SERVER[HTTP_HOST]/activate/?id=$prID</p>
      <p>The request will only be active for 12 hours. If you are unable to complete the process in that time you may make another request.</p>
  </body>
</html>
